# #Misfits Add - Paracusia perk localization. Kept thematically distinct from
# stealthboy-hallucinations.ftl so the two systems don't produce overlapping lines.

paracusia-hallucination-1 = Did someone just call your name?
paracusia-hallucination-2 = A door creaks behind you, but no one is there.
paracusia-hallucination-3 = You catch the tail end of a conversation that nobody is having.
paracusia-hallucination-4 = A chair scrapes across tile, somewhere just out of sight.
paracusia-hallucination-5 = You hear breathing right next to your ear.
paracusia-hallucination-6 = A radio you don't own crackles to life for half a second.
paracusia-hallucination-7 = Glass shatters in another room. There is no other room.
paracusia-hallucination-8 = You think you heard your own voice, talking to itself.
paracusia-hallucination-9 = A child laughs, very faintly, very far away.
paracusia-hallucination-10 = Tap. Tap. Tap. Tap.
paracusia-hallucination-11 = Was that a song? You can't quite remember it.
paracusia-hallucination-12 = Footsteps on metal. Coming closer. Then nothing.

paracusia-whisper-0 = ...behind you...
paracusia-whisper-1 = ...stop pretending you can't hear us...
paracusia-whisper-2 = ...turn around...
paracusia-whisper-3 = ...we're so close now...
paracusia-whisper-4 = ...you left it on, didn't you...
paracusia-whisper-5 = ...don't tell anyone...
paracusia-whisper-6 = ...one more step...
paracusia-whisper-7 = ...you forgot already...


trait-name-TraitParacusia = Paracusia
trait-description-TraitParacusia =
    You hear things that aren't there. Whispers, footsteps, voices calling your name —
    sometimes even snippets of conversations that never happened. Harmless to your body,
    but it grows worse the longer you stay conscious.
